{"tid":625794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【準備半年】丹麥爆破專家拆53米高筒倉　計錯數砸爛圖書館","createTime":"2018-04-11T17:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T11:03:04.000Z","uid":24309,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c59de8d57aebbf8643f51ade96f87b02c886b476","tid":625794,"uid":24309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T17:37:42.000Z","msg":"【準備半年】丹麥爆破專家拆53米高筒倉　計錯數砸爛圖書館<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1347503/org/ef8760c332b3de025e0ea46fd4bf4c65.png/EPgW_4eJwHqw6-7WMZTpQbx2KRIuKdPx75sFRe-bBUU?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1347503%2Forg%2Fef8760c332b3de025e0ea46fd4bf4c65.png%2FEPgW_4eJwHqw6-7WMZTpQbx2KRIuKdPx75sFRe-bBUU%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=6e854736&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當你找來一班觀眾欣賞自己表演，但途中出事，究竟會有多醜？丹麥最近有一個約53米高的老舊圓型筒倉（Silo）要拆除，當局找來一班爆破專家進行拆除作業。工程當日，有一班市民獲邀前來觀賞。工程人員甫按鈕，筒倉內部發生爆炸，但上半部分沒傾斜向預定位置，竟反方向砸落另一邊的圖書館，壓毀一角。幸好旁邊圖書館的職員都跑來湊熱鬧，所以事件中無人傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1347517/org/494c81a3a91c14c0cbc004148859948f.png/25s09GN4sXHfJ1VssLyatBsqSP9j_sn5eiG76Xohu-k?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1347517%2Forg%2F494c81a3a91c14c0cbc004148859948f.png%2F25s09GN4sXHfJ1VssLyatBsqSP9j_sn5eiG76Xohu-k%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=7e8ea88c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影片所見，工程人員按下引爆鈕後，現場市民一片歡呼，大家原以為筒倉會倒向左方空地，但疑因計算錯誤，斷裂的上半部份倒向右方的圖書館，市民不停高呼：「Oh! No!」結果旁邊的圖書館被砸爛一角。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幸好當日附近的居民連同圖書館內的人，都撤離到戶外觀看爆炸，未有人命傷亡。圖書館的受損區域為辦公室，大廈內散落的書籍、文件全被爆破粉塵覆蓋，經檢查後確定圖書館的建築結構未有損毀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n丹麥政府將圖書館在內的文化中心園封鎖，以確定其餘建築物的受損情況，確保安全才會開放予職員入內整理及進行維修，目前已派消防員徹夜駐守。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當地政府正調查出事原因，而丹麥炸藥協會認為，拆樓用的炸藥似乎正常，為何會炸歪需進一步研究。主理工程的爆破專家Kenneth Wegge稱難料事情會變得如此糟糕，強調「我們已經為此準備了半年」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sdD7R4bchB8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsdD7R4bchB8&d=2g5ryAzS6qBpMg3h1f8ErMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=e308c275\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sdD7R4bchB8</a>"},{"pid":"7f2dc54ed9395de618ba5c680b047e1a227fdc4d","tid":625794,"uid":29464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T17:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ee948649379d2e005f895dfc0913700336b225","tid":625794,"uid":1393,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T18:02:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">幸好當日附近的居民連同圖書館內的人，都撤離到戶外觀看爆炸</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78e4608205f560a879491abbcf0890990a66dd50","tid":625794,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T18:21:41.000Z","msg":"Lmao"},{"pid":"eec9bda0ef19089625950ec76eb52285fc29ab3c","tid":625794,"uid":973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T18:26:07.000Z","msg":"斜斜下左又去番右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680442ad6723ff1c0ee07daeaed533769381aa73","tid":625794,"uid":146243,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T18:32:39.000Z","msg":"個專家係現場嗰度實心諗：屌你老母 唔係咁玩我下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b792f8a8385763d1a281fb1c9cea10909c1d218e","tid":625794,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T18:57:14.000Z","msg":"準備半年, 但無計<br />\n南北極磁場開始掉轉丫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1db99e981dec77ea9cd9e4b0a017590fcc8c2a","tid":625794,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T19:08:00.000Z","msg":"似係下半部頂住左, 頂左向右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f13b3e2fd3c1925fe3c445f999eef93472ed27ce","tid":625794,"uid":15212